.83l67.2-67.19c28.239-28.239 74.3-28.069 102.325.51 27.75 28.3 26.872 73.934-1.155 101.96l-13.087 13.087c-4.35 4.35-5.769 10.79-3.783 16.612 5.864 17.194 9.042 34.999 9.69 52.721.509 13.906 17.454 20.446 27.294 10.606l37.106-37.106c59.271-59.259 59.271-155.699.001-214.959z\"/></svg>\n</span></a>\n    <a class=\"tweet-header\" href=\"https://twitter.com/alexand_erleon\" target=\"_blank\">\n      <b><img src=\"/tweets/alexand_erleon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></b>\n      <strong>\n        Alexander Leon\n        <i class=\"tweet-verified\">&nbsp;</i>\n        \n      </strong>\n      <span>@alexand_erleon</span>\n      <img src=\"/tweets/logo.svg\" alt=\"Twitter Logo\" class=\"tweet-logo\">\n    </a>\n    \n    \n     <div class=\"tweet-text\"><p>Queer people don't grow up as ourselves, we grow up playing a version of ourselves that sacrifices authenticity to minimise humiliation &amp; prejudice. The massive task of our adult lives is to unpick which parts of ourselves are truly us &amp; which parts we've created to protect us.</p></div>\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"tweet-footer\">\n      <a class=\"tweet-date\" href=\"https://twitter.com/alexand_erleon/status/1214459404575100928\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"2020-01-07T08:11:00.000Z\">4:11 PM - Tue, Jan 7th, 2020</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"tweet-item\" data-id=\"1214461916694736896\">\n    <a class=\"tweet-link\" href=\"https://twitter.com/alexand_erleon/status/1214461916694736896\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"svg-icon\" style=\"\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M326.612 185.391c59.747 59.809 58.927 155.698.36 214.59-.11.12-.24.25-.36.37l-67.2 67.2c-59.27 59.27-155.699 59.262-214.96 0-59.27-59.26-59.27-155.7 0-214.96l37.106-37.106c9.84-9.84 26.786-3.3 27.294 10.606.648 17.722 3.826 35.527 9.69 52.721 1.986 5.822.567 12.262-3.783 16.612l-13.087 13.087c-28.026 28.026-28.905 73.66-1.155 101.96 28.024 28.579 74.086 28.749 102.325.51l67.2-67.19c2