com/alexand_erleon/status/1214462851097608193\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"svg-icon\" style=\"\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M326.612 185.391c59.747 59.809 58.927 155.698.36 214.59-.11.12-.24.25-.36.37l-67.2 67.2c-59.27 59.27-155.699 59.262-214.96 0-59.27-59.26-59.27-155.7 0-214.96l37.106-37.106c9.84-9.84 26.786-3.3 27.294 10.606.648 17.722 3.826 35.527 9.69 52.721 1.986 5.822.567 12.262-3.783 16.612l-13.087 13.087c-28.026 28.026-28.905 73.66-1.155 101.96 28.024 28.579 74.086 28.749 102.325.51l67.2-67.19c28.191-28.191 28.073-73.757 0-101.83-3.701-3.694-7.429-6.564-10.341-8.569a16.037 16.037 0 0 1-6.947-12.606c-.396-10.567 3.348-21.456 11.698-29.806l21.054-21.055c5.521-5.521 14.182-6.199 20.584-1.731a152.482 152.482 0 0 1 20.522 17.197zM467.547 44.449c-59.261-59.262-155.69-59.27-214.96 0l-67.2 67.2c-.12.12-.25.25-.36.37-58.566 58.892-59.387 154.781.36 214.59a152.454 152.454 0 0 0 20.521 17.196c6.402 4.468 15.064 3.789 20.584-1.731l21.054-21.055c8.35-8.35 12.094-19.239 11.698-29.806a16.037 16.037 0 0 0-6.947-12.606c-2.912-2.005-6.64-4.875-10.341-8.569-28.073-28.073-28.191-73.639 0-101.83l67.2-67.19c28.239-28.239 74.3-28.069 102.325.51 27.75 28.3 26.872 73.934-1.155 101.96l-13.087 13.087c-4.35 4.35-5.769 10.79-3.783 16.612 5.864 17.194 9.042 34.999 9.69 52.721.509 13.906 17.454 20.446 27.294 10.606l37.106-37.106c59.271-59.259 59.271-155.699.001-214.959z\"/></svg>\n</span></a>\n    <a class=\"tweet-header\" href=\"https://twitter.com/alexand_erleon\" target=\"_blank\">\n      <b><img src=\"/tweets/alexand_erleon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></b>\n      <strong>\n        Alexander Leon\n        <i class=\"tweet-verified\">&nbsp;</i>\n        \n      </strong>\n      <span>@alexand_erleon</span>\n      <img src=\"/tweets/logo.svg\" alt=\"Twitter Logo\" class=\"tweet-logo\">\n    </a>\n    \n    \n     <div class=\"tweet-text\"><p>All of this is to say - be kind to yourself. Discovering who you really are is an enormous task it doesn't happen overnight, nor does it happen without some hiccups along the way. Be patient, be compassionate, be vulnerable and exist loudly. And most of all - be proud! <img class=\"emoji\" draggable=\"false\" alt=\"🏳️‍🌈\" src=\"https://twemoji.maxcdn.com/v/14.0.2/72x72/1f3f3-fe0f-200d-1f308.png\"/></p></div>\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"tweet-footer\">\n      <a class=\"tweet-date\" href=\"https://twitter.com/alexand_erleon/status/1214462851097608193\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"2020-01-07T08:24:41.000Z\">4:24 PM - Tue, Jan 7th, 2020</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"tweet-item\" data-id=\"1215568962139893760\">\n    <a class=\"tweet-link\" href=\"https://twitter.com/alexand_erleon/status/1215568962139893760\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"svg-icon\" style=\"\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M326.612 185.391c59.747 59.809 58.927 155.698.36 214.59-.11.12-.24.25-.36.37l-67.2 67.2c-59.27 59.27-155.699 59.262-214.96 0-59.27-59.26-59.27-155.7 0-214.96l37.106-37.106c9.84-9.84 26.786-3.3 27.294 10.606.648 17.722 3.826 35.527 9.69 52.721 1.986 5.822.567 12.262-3.783 16.612l-13.087 13.087c-28.026 28.026-28.905 73.66-1.155 101.96 28.024 28.579 74.086 28.749 102.325.51l67.2-67.19c28.191-28.191 28.073-73.757 0-101.83-3.701-3.694-7.429-6.564-10.341-8.569a16.037 16.037 0 0 1-6.947-12.606c-.396-10.567 3.348-21.456 11.698-29.806l21.054-21.055c5.521-5.521 14.182-6.199 20.584-1.731a152.482 152.482 0 0 1 20.522 17.197zM467.547 44.449c-59.261-59.262-155.69-59.27-214.96 0l-67.2 67.2c-.12.12-.25.25-.36.37-58.566 58.892-59.387 154.781.36 214.59a152.454 152.454 0 0 0 20.521 17.196c6.402 4.468 15.064 3.789 20.584-1.731l21.054-21.055c8.35-8.35 12.094-19.239 11.698-29.806a16.037 16.037 0 0 0-6.947-12.606c-2.912-2.005-6.64-4.875-10.341-8.569-28.073-28.073-28.191-73.639 0-101.83l67.2-67.19c28.239-28.239 74.3-28.069 102.325.51 27.75 28.3 26.872 73.934-1.155 101.96l-13.087 13.087c-4.35 4.35-5.769 10.79-3.783 16.612 5.864 17.194 9.042 34.999 9.69 52.721.509 13.906 17.454 20.446 27.294 10.606l37.106-37.106c59.271-59.259 59.271-155.699.001-214.959z\"/></svg>\n</span></a>\n    <a class=\"tweet-header\" href=\"https://twitter.com/alexand_erleon\" target=\"_blank\">\n      <b><img src=\"/tweets/alexand_erleon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></b>\n      <strong>\n        Alexander Leon\n        <i class=\"tweet-verified\">&nbsp;</i>\n        \n      </strong>\n      <span>@alexand_erleon</span>\n      <img src=\"/tweets/logo.svg\" alt=\"Twitter Logo\" class=\"tweet-logo\">\n    </a>\n    \n    \n     <div class=\"tweet-text\"><p>I've been so inspired by all your responses that I decided to publish the original essay that my recent tweets were adapted from. I'm a bit nervous about publishing something so personal, but I hope it speaks to someone out there.<img class=\"emoji\" draggable=\"false\" alt=\"❤️\" src=\"https://twemoji.maxcdn.com/v/14.0.2/72x72/2764.png\"/><img class=\"emoji\" draggable=\"false\" alt=\"🏳️‍🌈\" src=\"https://twemoji.maxcdn.com/v/14.0.2/72x72/1f3f3-fe0f-200d-1f308.png\"/></p><p><a href=\"https://medium.com/@alxndrleon/out-of-the-closet-and-into-the-fire-how-i-stopped-performing-and-learned-to-become-myself-6ff0dca4463d\" class=\"url\">medium.com/@alxndrleon/ou…</a></p></div>\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"tweet-footer\">\n      <a class=\"tweet-date\" href=\"https://twitter.com/alexand_erleon/status/1215568962139893760\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"2020-01-10T09:39:59.000Z\">5:39 PM - Fri, Jan 10th, 2020</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n</div>\n\n"}